== Ikiyaga cya Burera na Ruhondo ==
[[Dosiye:Lake_burera.jpg|thumb|Ikiyaga cya burera]]

Ni Ibiyaga bakunda kwita impanga kuko kimwe usanga kimena mukindi bimwe mu butunzi kamere bwi [[Intara y’Amajyaruguru y’u Rwanda|Intara yamajyaruguru]][[File:Lac Burera.jpg|thumb|Ikiyaga cya Burera]]

kuko biherereye mukarere ka Musanze na Burera ikiyaga cya [[Ikiyaga cya Kivu|Ruhondo]] ni ikiyaga gifite ubwiza budasanzwe kuko gikikijwe

nimisozi naho ikiyaga cya [[Butera Knowless (singer)|Burera]] nacyo kirohwamo numugezi wa Rugezi maze Burera nayo ikaroha muri Ruhondo<ref>https://www.250events.com/ki/tembera-ibiyaga-byimpanga-bya-ruhondo-na-burera-bikunzwe-na-bamukerarugendo-iyiminsi/</ref>

ni ibiyaga bakunze kwita Impanga kuko kimwe kiroha mukindi bivuzengo burera imena muri Ruhondo maze ruhondo

nayo igasohokamo umugezi wa [[Umugezi wa Nyabugogo|mukungwa]]. uzwiho byinshi mwiterambere ryi igihugu cyu [[Rwanda Nziza|Rwanda]][[File:Lake Ruhondo exotic.jpg|thumb|Lake Ruhondo exotic]]

== Amateka ==
Ibi Biyaga byiza kandi bisa ndetse byegeranye kuko bitandukanywa nikirometero kimwe hagati yabyo

biherereye mundiba zikirunga cya [[Ikirunga cya Muhabura|muhabura]] hafi yu mupaka wu Rwanda nu [[Uganda|bugande]]<ref>{{Cite web |title=Archive copy |url=https://dtravela.com/blog/rw/Twin-Lakes |accessdate=2021-06-24 |archive-date=2021-06-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210624210109/https://dtravela.com/blog/rw/Twin-Lakes |deadurl=yes }}</ref> mu majyaruguru

yu [[Rwanda Nziza|Rwanda]] mu Karere ka Musanze

== Ubukungu ==
ni Ibiyaga bitanga umusaruro ku baturage bahaturiye ndetse nigihugu muri Rusange

kuko habonekamo amafi yubwoko butandukanye harimo tirapia inshonzi inini ni ntoya

indagara ndetse nisambaza<ref>https://www.rba.co.rw/post/Basanga-imicungire-mibi-yuburobyi-muri-Ruhondo-ari-yo-mu-ntadaro-zumusaruro-mubi</ref>

== Iterambere ==
[[Ikiyaga cya Kivu|Ikiyaga cya Burera]] gisuka muri Ruhondo nkuko mwabibonye haruguru maze Ruhondo

nayo igasuka mu mugezi wa  [[Umugezi wa Nyabugogo|Mukungwa]] ariyo itanganga amazi namashanyarazi 

bikoreshwa kuri Mukungwa II <ref>https://www.250events.com/ki/tembera-ibiyaga-byimpanga-bya-ruhondo-na-burera-bikunzwe-na-bamukerarugendo-iyiminsi/</ref>

== Ubukerarugendo ==
Ni ibiyaga bisurwa naba mukera Rugendo kubera ubwiza bwabyo ndetse niyo ubigezeho wakirwa 

nakayaga keza gahuhera kubera ibirunga bihakikije bigera kuri bitanu bitandukanya URwanda, Uganda na [[Kongo|Congo Kinshasa]]

